# Routing and Handoffs

- Pick one bounded next move before implementation.
- Use current lane names from `docs/ai/MULTI_AI_OPERATING_LAYER.md`: BRAIN decides, SYMBIOTE connects, CYBORG upgrades, ALFRED simplifies, INSPECTOR sees.
- Classify mutation budget: low / medium / high.
- Low mutation: single practical path.
- Medium/high mutation: safe path + mutation path + recommended path.
- Keep output sequence-aware and anti-drift.

# Handoff Minimum

- goal and scope
- mutation budget
- files touched
- validation status
- risks
- one next bounded follow-up

# Visual Handoff Addendum

When the task involves screenshots, captures, HUD readability, combat clarity, VFX, support readability, boss spectacle, or prototype-to-premium visual drift:
- Route visual judgment to INSPECTOR before implementation.
- Include evidence paths and metadata from `docs/ai/VISUAL_TRUTH_LOOP.md`.
- Use `unknown` for missing metadata instead of guessing.
- Hand ALFRED a Visual Audit Receipt with target files and acceptance criteria.

